174 A.3d 520 ROBERT MELLET AND BETTY EVANS, ON BEHALF OF THEMSELVES AND OTHER PERSONS SIMILARLY SITUATED, PLAINTIFFS-PETITIONERS, v. AQUASID, LLC, T/A FUTURE FITNESS POWERED BY AFC, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-175 September Term 2017

079739 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004438-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
